  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [ ] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (8478c08 2022-05-05T06:20:40.607851+00:00)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (M1)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nIf the dependency in the lib directory is a symlink to a directory, forge infers default `lib` and `src` directories. It should follow the symlink and read any existing `foundry.toml`.",
