    "body": "say the dependency is `lib/dep --> ~/path/to/dep`, and `~/path/to/dep/foundry.toml` contains `src='src2'`. Then `forge config` will show `dep/=lib/dep/src/`. But if you copy over the actual folder, `forge config` will show `dep/=lib/dep/src2/`.",
